                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>At AbbVie, precision medicine is being used across the portfolio to bring medicines to the right patients using advanced technologies and data science to gain unprecedented insights into disease mechanism and patient heterogeneity. Our insights help us to target medicines more precisely, identify opportunities for combinations and provide patients and their physicians with actionable diagnostic tools. We are dedicated to understanding disease and addressing underlying mechanisms in all patients.&lt;/p>"/>
